column2: The land of milk and cookies
He who controls the cookies controls the universe - "The milk must flow!"
Are you gonna eat all that?
We're gonna need a bigger bakery
In the mouth of madness - "A cookie is just what we tell each other it is."
Brought to you by the letter Money
The dreams in which I'm baking are the best I've ever had
I think it's safe to say you've got it made
Not enough of a good thing
